# There are 100 cars available.
# There are only 30 drivers available.
# There will be 70 cars which can't be driven today.
# We can transport 120.0 people today.
# We have 90 who need to carpool today.
# We will put 3 in each car.
#
# The variable car_pool_capacity is not the same as carpool_capacity.
